# 通用短版 .gitignore(init.sh 鋪出時會改名為 .gitignore)。
# stack-specific 的規則(例:*.pyc、.next/、target/)由 scaffolder 或 AI 依專案補上。

# OS junk
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

# Editors(.vscode/ 不 ignore,常有共享設定)
.idea/
*.swp

# Secrets
.env
.env.*
!.env.example

# 常見依賴/build 產物
node_modules/
dist/
build/
__pycache__/
.venv/

# Logs
*.log

# Claude Code runtime state. `.claude/` itself IS tracked on purpose:
# kit-owned files are regenerable via `init.sh --update`, but settings.json
# (accumulated permission approvals) and protected-paths (project no-touch
# zones) are project truth that nothing can rebuild. Only machine-local
# state is excluded.
.claude/settings.local.json
.claude/scheduled_tasks.lock
